    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>For general information about getting support, see the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662089/Getting+Support\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662089\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Getting Support</a> page. </p><h2 id=\"ReportingBugs-ReproducingIssues/Bugs\">Reproducing Issues/Bugs</h2><p>When reporting issues or bugs, more often than not, we will require a method to reproduce the issue. This usually means we will need to see your files/assets.</p><p>In RfB, there is a convenient Package Scene button that can be used to package your files together ready to be sent to RenderMan Support. </p><h3 id=\"ReportingBugs-DebugLogging\">Debug Logging</h3><p>For crashes, RfB can log your render session to a debug python file. To start a log, turn on Debug Logging in the render properties tab as seen in the image below.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"2c2600db-5d3d-474a-a124-7c6d287d07dd\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>This option has to be turned on <strong>before</strong> rendering has started</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"debug_logging.png\" width=\"407\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/debug_logging.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754585878692&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=407&amp;height=291\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640138/debug_logging.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754585878692&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"291\" data-width=\"407\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546865176\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"debug_logging.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640138\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"2dc34488-fd76-4ab0-be62-e889898aef27\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/debug_logging.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754585878692&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=407&amp;height=291 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/debug_logging.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754585878692&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=407&amp;height=291 1x\"></span><p>The log will be placed in the same directory as the current blend file (with a <strong>.debug.py</strong> file extension). Please ensure that the folder the current blend file is in is writable.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"615c95db-e4f8-437a-b737-a61070648754\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The logging file can take up a lot of disk space, especially for heavier scenes. You’ll want to make sure the option is turned off after you’ve finished generating the log file. </p></div></div><h3 id=\"ReportingBugs-PackageScene\">Package Scene</h3><p>To package your scene, in the viewport press the 'n' key. This should bring up the side menu.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"side_menu.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/side_menu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=431\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640138/side_menu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1436\" data-width=\"2528\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640178\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"side_menu.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640138\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"9a48fc7f-4c3c-4922-ad09-3b4cd9640b24\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/side_menu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=862 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/side_menu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=431 1x\"></span><p>Next, click on the Renderman tab.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"renderman_tab.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/renderman_tab.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=507\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640138/renderman_tab.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1417\" data-width=\"2123\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640172\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"renderman_tab.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640138\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"ffd2ed31-0a71-44c5-a8ec-1e9046a0edea\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/renderman_tab.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=1014 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/renderman_tab.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432727621&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=507 1x\"></span><p>Under Utilities, click the Package Scene button. This will bring up a file browser.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"package_scene_options.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/package_scene_options.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754586254769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=599\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640138/package_scene_options.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754586254769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"836\" data-width=\"1059\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546963468\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"package_scene_options.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640138\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"94b98807-15ab-490d-9cd2-23b5f2ea9029\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/package_scene_options.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754586254769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1059&amp;height=836 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640138/package_scene_options.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1754586254769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=599 1x\"></span><p>Select a new or an existing empty directory, and then click Package Scene. The directory should now contain a new ZIP file, which you can then send in with your bug report. </p><h4 id=\"ReportingBugs-Options:\">Options:</h4><ul><li><p><strong>Include Blend File</strong>: this includes the .blend file with the ZIP package</p></li><li><p><strong>Include Debug Log: </strong>include the logging .debug.py file with the ZIP package, if it exists.</p></li><li><p><strong>Use RenderMan Textures: </strong>this replaces all of the texture file paths with the equivalent RenderMan .tex textures in the scene. </p></li></ul><p />"
    }
  },
